      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HASTY HOLLY (1) box seated before sticking on well to finish 6 lengths away in second (44.28) at this track in a Grade 6 over 730m. Rates highly and will give a great sight. ADHANA MADI (4) latest effort finished 3rd in a Free For All on July 16 over 730m at this track behind Lil Rex beaten 11 lengths (43.64). Can hit the frame with the right run. DOLAN (7) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 10 lengths into second (43.57) at this track in a Free For All over 730m. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from five attempts. Hard to beat again. MOSCOW CHICK (5) can measure up with the right run.",
